{"type": "article", "id": 3036, "title": "上发条的莫扎特音乐盒", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-24T07:30:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233005cHAgKnISWU1xOeb9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p>\r\n\t\t来自德国的工业设计师 Adam 与 Harborth 是狂热的莫扎特粉丝，这份喜爱促成了两人设计一款特别的音乐盒的想法，原理像极了我们童年时期都曾拥有过的八音盒。Adam 与 Harborth 将音乐盒设计成了一个实木球的样子，直径仅为 9.2 厘米，单手就能将其握在手中。实木球选取了来自德国西南部森林里的浅色山毛榉与深色橡木材质，并为其加入了涂蜡工艺，然后再搭配一个发条装置，拧上几圈，便可以听到莫扎特的音乐了。橡木款定价 69.5 欧元，山毛榉款定价 59.5 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.siebensachen.com/product_categories/view/6/142\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330042dok1hLF8Zqn6Vpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233004BOtk9sY64ZKmW5eS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233004m0kqUJfnz9wMbaYA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}